@startuml
title ProductType Lifecycle State (Implemented Baseline)

[*] --> Draft : create form opened
Draft --> Persisted : POST succeeds
Draft --> Draft : validation error

Persisted --> Persisted : GET/list/view
Persisted --> Updated : PUT succeeds
Updated --> Persisted : refresh list

Persisted --> Deleted : DELETE succeeds
Deleted --> [*]

Persisted --> Persisted : duplicate code rejected

@enduml
